                <head>No. 131.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#center">[Telegram from President of Ecuador to Ecuadorian
                        minister, dated <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-06-24">24th June,
                            1885</date>, and shown to Mr. Bayard by Señor Flores, 25th June,
                        1885.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have decided to ask from Congress pardon, in order to save Santos. Suspend
                    everything and answer.</p>
            </div>
